Task: Implement Small Standard Widget (2x2 Grid)

Summary: Implemented SmallStandardWidgetView with a 2x2 LazyVGrid layout displaying up to 4 habits. Each cell shows the habit's SF Symbol icon inside a WidgetCompletionRing (a new static ring component sized for widget contexts). The view includes completion state detection, empty state handling, and follows Stealth Ceramic theming.

Files Created:
- ductiva/SmallStandardWidgetView.swift (SmallStandardWidgetView + WidgetCompletionRing)
- ductivaTests/SmallStandardWidgetTests.swift (13 unit tests)

Files Modified:
- ductiva.xcodeproj/project.pbxproj (added SmallStandardWidgetView to ductivaWidgets target)

Why: Phase 3 requires implementing the small standard widget that displays up to 4 habits in a grid layout matching the design inspiration.
